{"tid":399790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"氣槍狂徒再挑戰警方 警車一出警署即遭狙擊","createTime":"2017-09-14T09:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T19:30:33.000Z","uid":119494,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"532d8c1992083cbbe96b008255890638b6bf006f","tid":399790,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"氣槍狂徒再度挑戰警方，再有警車遭BB彈射擊。中午12時43分，一輛灣仔分區警署警車駛出跑馬地成和道60號跑馬地警署，準備前往調查銅鑼灣一宗搶劫案，甫駛出門口，擋風玻璃即被氣槍子彈打中，並出現裂痕。警車車長指子彈是一粒黃色BB彈，車長事後留在現場向同袍提供資料協助調查，車上兩名警員則轉乘其他警車繼續前往查案。<br />\n<br />\n今次已是一個月內第二宗警車遭氣槍射擊事件，上月17日，一名女警駕駛警車駛至北角渣華道近電廠街時，遭氣槍射擊，警車右邊車門的玻璃應聲爆裂，並留下一個彈孔以及一粒鋼珠，該案無人被捕。警方正調查兩案是否同一狂徒所為，以及其動機為何。"},{"pid":"b1c374801ca50c9ac21f06e1e37d91454f027e79","tid":399790,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"追擊8月15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d711b32dac7d5b19b81648b137d73ef497a232","tid":399790,"uid":110832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"冇做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd6bc81b894d33398451a7737ded556349a3c39","tid":399790,"uid":5490,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"bb彈係市民愛黨愛國既延伸"},{"pid":"db27ec5e8030fc69bdbe246e0a3bc31370bd2caf","tid":399790,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bb彈係市民愛黨愛國既延伸</blockquote><br />\n愛的發射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c8139df7071c116f7616d8c43cbcae12c359c2","tid":399790,"uid":82929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入返支真槍先啦"},{"pid":"2e8ee50a214b1327c928045b648